{"type":"message","id":"1266db0a","parentId":"31f22208","timestamp":"2026-04-23T08:10:38.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我来直接生成这张图。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d3efc10481969f798fc587c0694e\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c9TYK2beKjs2VgKbHgISIsvD|fc_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d3f0cf5c81968636d285a4a8890e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/songci && bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '中国宋代词意境插画，表现《长相思·伤春》：暮春时节，小园寂寥，残花零落，细雨微寒，夜里东风吹过，女子倚窗难眠，隔着小阑有黄莺啼叫。远处柳丝低垂，天空有迟来的雁影，地上铺满带香气的落花尘泥。整体情绪是伤春、思人未归、清冷、含蓄、婉约。画面唯美，古典中国画与电影感融合，细节精致，柔和灰青与淡粉配色，雨后湿润空气感，诗意留白，无文字，无题字。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/songci/changxiangsi-shangchun.png --ar 4:3","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"background":true},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/songci && bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '中国宋代词意境插画，表现《长相思·伤春》：暮春时节，小园寂寥，残花零落，细雨微寒，夜里东风吹过，女子倚窗难眠，隔着小阑有黄莺啼叫。远处柳丝低垂，天空有迟来的雁影，地上铺满带香气的落花尘泥。整体情绪是伤春、思人未归、清冷、含蓄、婉约。画面唯美，古典中国画与电影感融合，细节精致，柔和灰青与淡粉配色，雨后湿润空气感，诗意留白，无文字，无题字。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/songci/changxiangsi-shangchun.png --ar 4:3\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":29606,"output":301,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29907,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776931820855,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d3ee2a5c81968b148751d28fae47"}}
