{"type":"message","id":"356b64ca","parentId":"da5b0a78","timestamp":"2026-04-23T08:15:05.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我先直接生成这张“手机随手拍餐巾纸素描”。前面那条 360° 巴黎全景你还没发完，我先不乱补全，等你把完整描述发来我再做。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d4fc482c8196a6aaffb5de48adc0\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mFFH982KFtodfH7ZN9uTi7x9|fc_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d4ff68cc819682b32ce105843558","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/sketch && bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '一张放在木桌上的白色餐巾纸，上面用铅笔速写一位长发女性的正面肖像，线条自然随意，像临时手绘。餐巾纸旁边有一圈淡淡的咖啡渍，桌面有真实木纹，整体像手机随手拍摄的生活瞬间照片，自然光，轻微透视，真实摄影质感，简洁构图，无文字。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/sketch/napkin-pencil-portrait.png --ar 4:3","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"background":true},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/sketch && bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '一张放在木桌上的白色餐巾纸，上面用铅笔速写一位长发女性的正面肖像，线条自然随意，像临时手绘。餐巾纸旁边有一圈淡淡的咖啡渍，桌面有真实木纹，整体像手机随手拍摄的生活瞬间照片，自然光，轻微透视，真实摄影质感，简洁构图，无文字。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/sketch/napkin-pencil-portrait.png --ar 4:3\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":31698,"output":278,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776932089308,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169e9d4fa85d08196a8af967084c55dfa"}}
