{"type":"message","id":"ed2a3327","parentId":"eef6f977","timestamp":"2026-04-23T12:22:37.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我直接给你生成这个场景版，把桌上的《静夜思》宣纸和“李白思乡”的氛围一起放进去。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea0efe0fb08196abb800db0c7f90e2\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0WMAomjyXJJULrRhDhKAQvs9|fc_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea0f0051f481968d131febe59dfe5b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '中国古风场景插画，桌上铺着一幅宣纸，上面用毛笔写着李白的《静夜思》，文字清晰可见：床前明月光，疑是地上霜。举头望明月，低头思故乡。旁边是毛笔、砚台与墨迹。画面中李白身穿唐代文人服饰，坐于桌旁，在夜色与月光下沉思故乡，神情含蓄忧思。室内古典雅致，窗外可见明月，整体有浓厚诗意与思乡氛围，中国传统国风插画风格，细节精致，宣纸质感明显，月光清冷柔和。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/text/libai-jingyesi-hometown-scene.png --ar 4:3","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"background":true},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"bun ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --prompt '中国古风场景插画，桌上铺着一幅宣纸，上面用毛笔写着李白的《静夜思》，文字清晰可见：床前明月光，疑是地上霜。举头望明月，低头思故乡。旁边是毛笔、砚台与墨迹。画面中李白身穿唐代文人服饰，坐于桌旁，在夜色与月光下沉思故乡，神情含蓄忧思。室内古典雅致，窗外可见明月，整体有浓厚诗意与思乡氛围，中国传统国风插画风格，细节精致，宣纸质感明显，月光清冷柔和。' --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/text/libai-jingyesi-hometown-scene.png --ar 4:3\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"background\":true}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":46683,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776946938577,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea0efc6dfc8196a96c348c8f50df00"}}
