{"type":"message","id":"c1f699e4","parentId":"ac9b4ae9","timestamp":"2026-04-23T12:38:29.816Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-23 20:23:28 GMT+8] Exec completed (mild-for, code 0) :: Using openai / gpt-image-2 for single Switch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-im…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776947906618-dee369a5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 20:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n生成一个马斯克正在抖音直播间卖加多宝凉茶的照片，要求逼真，直播间下面还有评论"}],"timestamp":1776947909765}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad30630f","parentId":"c1f699e4","timestamp":"2026-04-23T12:38:44.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，这种图我不能直接做，因为它同时涉及：\n- **真实公众人物**\n- **逼真照片风格**\n- 以及看起来像真实平台直播带货的场景，容易造成误导\n\n但我可以马上给你做一个很好玩的安全版本，比如：\n\n**可生成版本**\n“一个长相有科技创业者气质的中年男性，在短视频直播间里卖凉茶饮料，画面为高真实感但非真人复刻的影视海报风。直播间有补光灯、产品陈列、夸张的带货手势，屏幕下方有滚动评论弹幕，整体热闹、幽默、带一点网络直播荒诞感。”\n\n如果你愿意，我还能给你分成两种风格：\n1. **搞笑直播截图风**\n2. **高质感电影海报风**\n\n你回我：\n- **1**\n- **2**\n- 或者 **“直接生成你推荐的”**\n\n我就继续。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea12c8bc148196b2ee24adb00ae5e7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":48050,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776947909816,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea12c7333c81969845cc8595e005b0"}}
