{"type":"message","id":"a7de55fe","parentId":"8d7c9f8e","timestamp":"2026-04-23T12:48:29.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是一个 GitHub 仓库链接：\n\n**EvoLinkAI/awesome-gpt-image-2-prompts**  \n主要内容是整理好的 **GPT-Image-2 提示词案例库**，方向包括：\n- 人像\n- 海报\n- UI mockup\n- 角色设定图\n- 社区实验案例\n\n如果你是想让我帮你用它，我可以直接继续做这几种事里的一种：\n1. **帮你总结这个仓库里最值得抄的 prompt 结构**\n2. **挑出最适合你现在这类中文出图需求的模板**\n3. **把它改写成你能直接复制用的中文 prompt 套件**\n\n你回我一句：\n- **总结**\n- **改成中文模板**\n- **挑最实用的**  \n我就继续。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea1514214c8196b41013037e7f9e8f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":49227,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49412,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776948496900,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea15126d088196ad37467dff6ddabb"}}
