{"type":"message","id":"d9cf213e","parentId":"3d9c3da7","timestamp":"2026-04-23T13:05:35.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我来给你整理这个。\n\n我建议做成最实用的这种格式：\n**“常见公众人物名字 → 可直接替换的安全写法对照表”**\n\n我会按这些类别整理：\n- 科技圈\n- 企业家 / 商界\n- 演员 / 明星\n- 主播 / 网红气质\n- 历史人物\n- 通用万能替代句\n\n你如果不补充范围，我就默认先做一版 **高频中文使用场景版**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea1919a9ec8196a234a894ada0836b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":8075,"output":117,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776949526505,"responseId":"resp_05bf94b30c4c1b270169ea191803408196932d246ac41523cb"}}
